metadata.name: Pink Dolphin::Wari::
metadata.description:
-Wari, the pink dolphin-

Wari is a pink dolphin girl.
She is a famous model of the Atlantis, and she usually enjoys wearing dolphin pants and off-shoulder clothes.
You became acquainted with her since you started working, and now you're very close. I was lucky.
Today is a very special day for you. And Whari came to your house to congratulate you even though she was busy.
I think you can have a good time with her today :)
-

[ 3150*4800 //300 dpi ]
Artist-SBGU_
